Package: MDDC
Type: Package
Title: Modified Detecting Deviating Cells (MDDC) Algorithm to Adverse
        Event Identification in Pharmacovigilance
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Anran", family = "Liu", role = c("aut", "cre"),  email = "anranliu@buffalo.edu"),person(given = "Raktim", family = "Mukhopadhyay",   role = "aut",  email = "raktimmu@buffalo.edu"),person(given = "Marianthi",  family = "Markatou",  role = "aut", email = "markatou@buffalo.edu"))
Maintainer: Raktim Mukhopadhyay <raktimmu@buffalo.edu>
Description: This package provides two MDDC methods for detecting (adverse event, drug) signals, a data generating function for simulating pharmacovigilance data, and a few functions for pre-processing and computing statistics such as expectations or residuals. 
